examples.en: Scientists are concerned about ozone depletion.
We completely depleted our life savings when we bought our new house.

examples.en: Compute depletion and journalize entry for depletion.

examples.en: Activities such as logging and mining deplete our natural resources.
examples.ru: Такие виды деятельности, как вырубка леса и добыча руды, истощают наши природные ресурсы.
